Privacy Policy

Activity Diary Debug and its authors have a deep interest to respect your privacy. The nature of this app is to track and store your activites and where and how you do them. Nevertheless it is your data in your hands and is not transmitted to any server or external party by the app without your explicit request. Read the full privacy policy.

Contact

For bugs and suggestions use the issue tacker, preferably in English language.

Source code can be found on Github.

Support

In case you want to support the development of Activity Diary Debug consider discussing issues on github, translating on crowdin or donation on Liberapay.
